reviewText: it was in good shape played good great artist recieved quickly liked every thing no dislikes i will recommened you

If you like Destiny's Child music videos then you'll like this. Here are the tracks:

Lose My Breath Video Megamix by Destiny's Child

Survivor by Destiny's Child

Emotion by Destiny's Child

Can't Nobody by Kelly Rowland

Do You Know by Michelle Williams

Me, Myself, and I by Beyonce

The Lose My Breath video has the audio from Lose My Breath but instead of the actual video it shows clips from other Destiny's Child videos. By the way, the package says "A Wal-Mart Exclusive" and I got this new for five dollars.
